# Smart Attendance System вЂ“ Version 1

Smart Attendance System is an IoT-based attendance tracking solution using **ESP32, RFID, Firebase, and a Web Dashboard**.

Employees scan their RFID cards, and attendance is recorded automatically in **Firebase Realtime Database** and displayed on a **live web dashboard**.

This project is **Version 1 (V1)** of the system and focuses on building the **core attendance workflow and dashboard interface**.


# Features (V1)

### RFID Attendance

* Scan RFID card using ESP32
* Read UID of card
* Send UID to Firebase
* Automatically mark attendance

### Employee Management

* Add employees
* Assign RFID UID
* Edit employee details
* Delete employees

### Live Dashboard

* Total employees
* Present employees today
* Absent employees today
* Attendance percentage chart
* Present employee list

### Activity Logs

* Records recent system activity
* Shows attendance events

### Device Status

* Shows ESP32 device status
* Online / Offline indicator

### Test Mode

* Scan RFID card to verify employee
* Displays employee name

### Reports

* Generate attendance report
* Select date range
* Export CSV
* Export JSON

### System Settings

* Reset today's attendance
* Clear attendance by date
* Reset all attendance data
* Restart ESP32
* Clear activity logs

